OL,3,CRoman altars acquired for nation to go
OL,4,Con show for first time
OL,6,FTwo "stunning" stone altars discovered
OL,7,Fat a Roman fort near Edinburgh and
OL,8,Facquired for the nation are to go on
OL,9,Fshow for the first time in a new
OL,10,Fexhibition.
OL,12,FThe altars were once the centrepiece
OL,13,Fof the most northerly temple to the
OL,14,Fgod Mithras known of in the Roman
OL,15,Fempire, and are said to "really bring
OL,16,Fthe beliefs of the Roman frontier to
OL,17,Flife".
