OL,3,CRoman altars acquired for nation to go
OL,4,Con show for first time
OL,6,FThey were acquired in 2016 by National
OL,7,FMuseums Scotland (NMS), who are
OL,8,Fsharing news of the acquisition for
OL,9,Fthe first time.
OL,11,FThe altars have since undergone
OL,12,Fextensive conservation work and will
OL,13,Fgo on show for the first time in
OL,14,FNovember in Roman Scotland: Life On
OL,15,FThe Edge Of Empire.
OL,17,FDr Fraser Hunter, principal curator of
OL,18,Fprehistory and Roman archaeology at
OL,19,FNMS,said:"These stunning altars
OL,20,Freally bring the beliefs of the Roman
OL,21,Ffrontier to life.
