OL,6,F"The quality of the carving, traces of
OL,7,Fpaint and dramatic lighting effects
OL,8,Fshow they were impressive and
OL,9,Fexpensive monuments.
OL,11,F"The cult of Mithras represented the
OL,12,Ftriumph of good over evil and gave
OL,13,Fsoldiers a sense that there was a
OL,14,Fpurpose to their world and a life
OL,15,Fafter death.
OL,17,F"I'm sure visitors will be amazed by
OL,18,Fthem when they can see them up close
OL,19,Fin our new exhibition, Roman Scotland:
OL,20,FLife On The Edge Of Empire."
