OL,4,Con show for first time
OL,6,FOne of the altars depicts the face of
OL,7,Fthe sun god Sol and also features
OL,8,Fcarvings of the four seasons, depicted
OL,9,Fas female deities.
OL,11,FCurators said it would have been
OL,12,Filluminated from behind so that in the
OL,13,Flow light of the temple, worshippers
OL,14,Fwould have seen Sol's eyes, mouth and
OL,15,Fthe rays of his solar crown glowing.
