OL,4,Con show for first time
OL,6,FDuring their time buried underground,
OL,7,Fthe altars, which were excavated in
OL,8,F2010, had broken into fragments and
OL,9,Fthey have undergone conservation work
OL,10,Fto reconstruct them and prepare them
OL,11,Ffor display.
OL,13,FWhile they were carrying out this work
OL,14,Fconservators identified traces of
OL,15,Fpaint on the carvings, revealing that
OL,16,Foriginally they would have been
OL,17,Fpainted in vibrant colours.
