OL,6,FThe exhibition Roman Scotland: Life On
OL,7,FThe Edge Of Empire at the National
OL,8,FMuseum of Scotland in Edinburgh will
OL,9,Faddress the common misconception that
OL,10,Fthe Romans never got beyond Hadrian's
OL,11,FWall.
OL,13,FExperts said the empire in fact
OL,14,Fextended its reach much further north
OL,15,Fthree times, up to Scotland's central
OL,16,Fbelt and deep into north-east Scotland.
