OL,6,FFortifications built by the Romans
OL,7,Fincluded the Antonine Wall which was
OL,8,Fconstructed across the narrowest part
OL,9,Fof Scotland from the Clyde to the
OL,10,FForth, with additional forts along the
OL,11,Fcoasts to the west and east including
OL,12,FInveresk.
OL,14,FIn the exhibition finds from Inveresk
OL,15,Fwill be displayed together for the
OL,16,Ffirst time.
