OL,6,FCurators said this will shed new light
OL,7,Fon the Roman occupation in Scotland,
OL,8,Fand demonstrate how this "significant
OL,9,Ffrontier outpost" was supplied from
OL,10,Facross the empire, and the impacts
OL,11,Fthis occupation had on the local
OL,12,Fpopulation.
OL,14,FRoman Scotland: Life On The Edge Of
OL,15,FEmpire will run from November 2026
OL,16,Funtil April 28 2027.
